extendedInfo.description: *** Requires ADW Launcher 1.3 or higher ***Enjoy my latest ADW theme inspired by the new sense ui dock, Sense Glass.- Specifically designed for 5 icon style- Same icon pack as another theme of mine "Black Glass"- Alternative launcher icon options (including a blank icon) in the icon pack- Only hdpi support for now

reviews.title: AWESOME!
reviews.comment: This theme is AWESOME! I LOVE LOVE LOVE how all icons on the quick launch bar can be customized).
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Icons need work :)
